I think this is racy as you may have `queue.offer` return false if this method is invoked by multiple threads.

You should do something like:
```java
void offerPastBufferSize(final Object signal, final ConcurrentLinkedQueue<Object> queue) {
    while (!queue.offer(signal)) {
        queue.poll();
    }
}
```

